What are the challenges faced in the MSHR market?
High treatment costs, regulatory hurdles, and potential side effects are major challenges in the MSHR market.

Which region dominates the MSHR market?
North America currently holds the largest share of the MSHR market, driven by advanced healthcare infrastructure and high research investment.

